When creating a pet, give one parameter:
        name

hunger, thirst and bored are set:

hunger: 20
thirst: 20 
bored: false
exerciseLevel: 0
maxExerciseLevel: 20
alive: true
age: 1
maxAge: 10

METHODS

feed()
    hunger++;
giveDrink()
    thirst++
play()
    if bored = true 
        return yay! let's play!
        bored = false; 
    else 
        return I don't feel like playing...
exercise()
    if exerciseLevel <= 0 && exerciseLevel <= 19
        exerciseLevel++
        hunger--
        thirst--
    else 
        return I've reached max buff! 
levelUp()
    if age <= 10
        age++
    else alive: false

checkHunger()
checkThirst()
checkExerciseLevel()


IF/ELSE 

if hunger < 0 && thirst < 0 
 alive: false

if hunger >= 0 && hunger <=10
    return I'm hungry...

if hunger >= 11 && hunger <= 15
    return I'm pretty full...

if hunger => 15 && hunger <=20
    return I'm full! 

